				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/#process">Sell Your House</a>
					<a href="/reviews/">Reviews</a>
					<a href="/faq/" aria-current="page">FAQ</a>
					<div class="language-switch" aria-label="Language options">
						<a href="/faq/" aria-current="page">EN</a>
						<a href="/es/faq/">ES</a>
					</div>
					<a href="tel:18636603118" class="nav-call">Call Now</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="faq-hero">
				<div class="faq-hero-inner">
					<p class="eyebrow">Frequently asked questions</p>
					<h1>Questions?</h1>
					<p>Answered by our folks at Amigos House Buyer, LLC</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="faq-section" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
				<div class="faq-list">
					<!-- Duplicate a details block below for each question and answer. -->
					<details>
						<summary> Q:  Will you actually buy our house?</summary>
						<p>
							Yes, we will!  If the house meets our criteria we proceed and buy it. You can, sell your house <b>fast</b>, in Lakeland, Plant City, Davenport, and surrounding areas. We don’t use bank financing so you don’t have to worry about our ability to close on a deal. After purchasing we update the house put it back on the market or keep it in our portfolio.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details>
						<summary>Q:  How are you different from a real estate agent?</summary>
						<p>
							We don't charge any fees. When we agree on price and terms we don't have to qualify to a Financial Institution.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details>
						<summary>Q: How much you pay for my house?</summary>
						<p>
							The price we are willing to pay for a house depends on the condition of the house and the values of the comparable houses in the vicinity. Our no-obligation pricing commitment means that you don’t have to move forward with the offer we give you.
							<br><br>Typically we offer two options: One cash option and the other option using financing.</br>
						</p>
					</details>

					<details>
						<summary>Q:  Are there any fees or commissions when working with AMIGOS HOUSE BUYER?</summary>
						<p>
							No fees or commissions when you sell directly to us, unlike listing fees that can take up to 6% from your pocket. We’ll make you an offer, and if it fits, we’ll buy your house commission-free. We often cover closing costs too! Once we buy, the burden is ours, and you walk away free from property responsibilities.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details>
						<summary>Q:  Is there any obligation when I submit my information?</summary>
						<p>
							There is absolutely zero obligation for you, we’ll run our numbers and let you know your options. From there, it’s 100% your decision on whether or not you’d like to sell your house to us. We’ll let you decide what’s right for you.
						</p>
					</details>
				</div>

				<aside class="faq-card" aria-label="Contact Amigos House Buyer">
					<p class="section-kicker">Still have questions?</p>
					<h2>Talk with us before you decide.</h2>
					<p>
						Call Amigos House Buyer and ask anything about the process, the offer, or your timeline.
					</p>
					<a class="button primary" href="tel:18636603118">Call 863 660 3118</a>
				</aside>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		color-scheme: light;
		font-family:
			Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
		--ink: #162317;
		--muted: #5d6570;
		--cream: #fff8ef;
		--orange: #fd8b17;
		--blue: #1164b0;
		--blue-dark: #083d72;
		--blue-soft: #e9f3ff;
		--white: #ffffff;
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	body {
		margin: 0;
		background: var(--cream);
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	a {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.site-header {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0 0 auto;
		z-index: 5;
	}

	.top-bar {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 18px;
		padding: 10px clamp(16px, 4vw, 48px);
		background: rgba(8, 61, 114, 0.97);
		color: var(--white);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.top-bar p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.top-bar a {
		color: var(--orange);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.nav {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 24px;
		width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 32px));
		margin: 18px auto 0;
		padding: 14px 18px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
		box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(8, 61, 114, 0.16);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
	}

	.brand {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		min-width: 150px;
	}

	.brand-logo {
		width: min(190px, 38vw);
		height: 56px;
		border-radius: 6px;
		object-fit: contain;
		object-position: left center;
		background: var(--blue-soft);
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: clamp(14px, 2.4vw, 28px);
		color: var(--blue-dark);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.nav-links [aria-current="page"] {
		color: var(--orange);
	}

	.nav-call {
		padding: 10px 14px;
		border-radius: 6px;
		background: var(--orange);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.language-switch {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		gap: 3px;
		padding: 3px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(17, 100, 176, 0.2);
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #eef6ff;
		box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
	}

	.language-switch a {
		display: inline-flex;
		min-width: 34px;
		min-height: 30px;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 999px;
		padding: 7px 10px;
		font-size: 0.76rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.language-switch [aria-current="page"] {
		background: var(--blue-dark);
		color: var(--white);
		box-shadow: 0 5px 14px rgba(8, 61, 114, 0.2);
	}

	.language-switch a:not([aria-current="page"]) {
		color: var(--blue-dark);
	}

	.language-switch a:not([aria-current="page"]):hover {
		background: rgba(253, 139, 23, 0.16);
		color: #9d4a00;
	}

	.faq-hero {
		padding: 185px clamp(18px, 6vw, 86px) 78px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(8, 61, 114, 0.94), rgba(17, 100, 176, 0.78)),
			url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570129477492-45c003edd2be?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=82")
				center / cover;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.faq-hero-inner {
		max-width: 920px;
	}

	.eyebrow,
	.section-kicker {
		color: var(--orange);
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		display: inline-flex;
		margin: 0 0 18px;
		padding: 8px 12px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
		color: #ffe4ca;
	}

	h1 {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5.2rem);
		line-height: 0.98;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	.faq-hero p:last-child {
		max-width: 680px;
		margin: 24px 0 0;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
		font-size: 1.12rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.faq-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(290px, 360px);
		gap: clamp(24px, 5vw, 58px);
		align-items: start;
		padding: clamp(54px, 7vw, 92px) clamp(18px, 6vw, 86px);
	}

	.faq-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 14px;
	}

	details {
		border: 1px solid #cfe2f5;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: var(--white);
		box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(8, 61, 114, 0.08);
	}

	summary {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 18px;
		padding: 22px 24px;
		color: var(--blue-dark);
		cursor: pointer;
		font-size: 1.12rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		list-style: none;
	}

	summary::-webkit-details-marker {
		display: none;
	}

	summary::after {
		display: grid;
		flex: 0 0 34px;
		width: 34px;
		height: 34px;
		place-items: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--blue-soft);
		color: var(--blue);
		content: "+";
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	details[open] summary::after {
		background: var(--orange);
		color: var(--white);
		content: "-";
	}

	details p {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0 24px 24px;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.75;
	}

	.faq-card {
		position: sticky;
		top: 22px;
		display: grid;
		gap: 16px;
		padding: 28px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: var(--blue-dark);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.faq-card h2,
	.faq-card p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.faq-card h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
		line-height: 1.05;
	}

	.faq-card p:not(.section-kicker) {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.button {
		display: inline-flex;
		min-height: 52px;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 6px;
		padding: 14px 20px;
		font-weight: 900;
	}

	.button.primary {
		background: var(--orange);
		color: #221104;
	}

	@media (max-width: 920px) {
		.nav {
			align-items: flex-start;
		}

		.nav-links {
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			justify-content: flex-end;
		}

		.faq-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.faq-card {
			position: static;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 680px) {
		.top-bar {
			display: grid;
			gap: 5px;
			padding-block: 8px;
		}

		.nav {
			margin-top: 10px;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 12px;
		}

		.nav-links {
			width: 100%;
			justify-content: space-between;
			gap: 8px;
			font-size: 0.82rem;
		}

		.nav-call {
			padding: 9px 11px;
		}

		.faq-hero {
			padding: 214px 16px 50px;
		}

		summary {
			padding: 19px 18px;
		}

		details p {
			padding: 0 18px 20px;
		}
	}
</style>
